column2: THE MOST THING THAT WE WANT IS CAPTAIN JACK SPARROW BACK IS JOHNNY DEPP BACK INTO THIS RIDE PIRATES OF THE CARIBBEAN
column33: Disney : Stop Disney removing Jack Sparrow!
column34:
Since amber heard has made her terrible claims and lies against Johnny Depp it’s been said he will lose his roles in fantastic beasts and pirates of the Caribbean. 
It’s also now been claimed Disney will be taking away our beloved Captain Jack Sparrow from their pirates of the Caribbean ride at their Disneyland parks. Captain Jack is everyone’s favourite pirate, and without him Pirates of the Caribbean wouldn’t be as great as what it is! 
Let’s get justice for Johnny Depp! Let us see him keep his movies we all love and his place in the Disneyland attraction!

The real perpetrator of Domestic Violence is Amber Heard, who should have to pay the consequences of her lies, gaslighting, deception, and manipulation.

Since amber heard has made her terrible claims and lies against Johnny Depp it’s been said he will lose his roles in fantastic beasts and pirates of the Caribbean. 
It’s also now been claimed Disney will be taking away our beloved Captain Jack Sparrow from their pirates of the Caribbean ride at their Disneyland parks. Captain Jack is everyone’s favourite pirate, and without him Pirates of the Caribbean wouldn’t be as great as what it is! 
Let’s get justice for Johnny Depp! Let us see him keep his movies we all love and his place in the Disneyland attraction!
